---
title: Barramundi Stir-Fry with Chow Mein Noodles and Garlicky Veggies
description: The sweet and savoury combination of hoisin and soy pair perfectly with succulent Barramundi. Even simpler than a stir-fry, saucy noodles, sweet and crunchy veggies and Barramundi come together with ease.
